{
  "stem": "11641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Especially, you know, especially males.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And if you had a Semitic look, you had no chance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that you were afraid of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, you were afraid of the Poles more than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would point out to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the tragedy of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we came to the United States on 16th of January, 1947.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my uncle and his daughter, my cousin, waited for us, who I've never met before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we waited almost all day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody was [INAUDIBLE] [LAUGHS] because everybody was-- came on the-- on the auspices of either joining the [INAUDIBLE] committee, or HIAS, or some other organizations.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we came private, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were the [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We were private, but eventually we made it, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] we took the cab to Penn Station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was passing by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I says, uncle-- because Jack Dempsey Russell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, uncle, this is the Jack Dempsey?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, you know about him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I says [LAUGHS] yeah, I know about him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we went to Penn Station and we want to-- to an office by the Long Island Railroad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we lived there for about a month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yes, my cousin that-- they wanted us live longer there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I said-- I said, look, I have enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I says, I'm married now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My wife is pregnant-- Sally was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, we lived for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my cousin, he didn't speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So she-- he tells her this-- tell him, they want-- he shouldn't rush so much to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Once he starts working, he never going to stop until he retire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So what is his rush?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He says, he likes it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He doesn't like it here?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
